name: Efficient Labor Operations
title: Streamlined Labor Regulations
description: In 2024, Morocco achieved an operational efficiency score of 32.17 in labor regulations and public services, indicating a streamlined approach to labor management.

name: Tariff-Free Zone
title: Minimal Tariff Lines on Products
description: As of 2021, Morocco had an impressively low share of tariff lines with specific rates, with only 0.0008% for all products and 0.0071% for primary products, promoting a more open trade environment.
